## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-198">추가할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection> 를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> 에서 메서드는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-198">You can add <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objects to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection> by using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> method on the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-199">초기화 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 개체 및 지정는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체는 인수로 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 자동으로 추가 되는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection> 에 대 한는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-199">If you initialize an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object and specify an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object as the argument, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> is automatically added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection> for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-200">다음 예에서는 구문을 인식 하는 문법을 "World Cup 성공한에 국가" World Cup 했습니다 국가의 이름이 차례로 나옵니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-200">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-201">이 예에서는 만듭니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 개체를 다음 이라는 공용 규칙을 만듭니다 `winnerRule`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-201">The example creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object, and then creates a public rule named `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-202">규칙에는 문자열을 추가한 후 `winnerRule`,이 예에서는 두 개 이상의 규칙을 만듭니다 (`ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica`), 각 국가 목록을 포함 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-202">After adding a string to the rule `winnerRule`, the example creates two more rules (`ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`), each containing a list of countries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-203">사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> 세 가지 규칙을 추가 하는 메서드를 예제 (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, 및 `ruleSAmerica`)에 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-203">Using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> method, the example adds all three rules (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, and `ruleSAmerica`) to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-212">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 개체를 다음 이라는 공용 규칙을 만듭니다 `winnerRule`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-212">The following example creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object, and then creates a public rule named `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-213">그런 다음 만듭니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> 는 문자열을 구성 하 "world cup 성공한에 국가:",이 항목을 추가 하 고는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> 규칙의 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-213">It then creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> that consists of the string "A nation that has won the world cup is:", and adds this item to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> property of the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-214">이 예에서는 다음 두 개 이상의 규칙을 만듭니다 (`ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica`), 각 되며이 중 한 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 3 개 포함 된 개체 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-214">The example then creates two more rules (`ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`), each of which is an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object that contains three <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-215">그런 다음 다른 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 개체가 포함 된 만들어집니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> 참조 하는 개체 `ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-215">After that, another <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object is created that contains <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> objects that refer to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-216">새 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 개체 다음에 추가 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> 속성 `winnerRule`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-216">The new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object is then added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> property of `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-217">이 세 가지 규칙 (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, 및 `ruleSAmerica`)에 추가 되는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-217">After this, all three rules (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, and `ruleSAmerica`) are added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-218">이 예에서는 빈 XML 파일 및의 인스턴스를 만듭니다 마지막으로, <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-218">Finally, the example creates an empty XML file and an instance of <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="69ad3-219"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.WriteSrgs%2A> 메서드는 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> 의 콘텐츠를 작성 하는 인스턴스는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> XML 파일에 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69ad3-219">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.WriteSrgs%2A> method uses the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance to write the contents of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> to the XML file.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
  
  // Create a string object with the path to the file to use.  
  string srgsDocumentFile = Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), "srgsDocumentFile.xml");  
  
  // Create an XmlWriter object and pass the file path.  
  XmlWriter writer = XmlWriter.Create(srgsDocumentFile);  
  
  // Write the contents of the XmlWriter object to an SRGS-compatible XML file.  
  document.WriteSrgs(writer);  
  writer.Close();  
}  
```
